Subject: [PATCH] pwm: imx27: Fix rounding behavior
Date:   Thu, 16 Apr 2020 10:02:45 +0200
Message-Id: <20200416080245.3203-1-u.kleine-koenig@pengutronix.de>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.26.0.rc2
